  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 400°F (200°C).",
    "In a small bowl, mix together savory seasoning, olive oil, and Egyptian spices.",
    "Place the chicken breast in a large baking dish and brush with the savory mixture.",
    "Arrange the juicy tomatoes, onion, and garlic around the chicken.",
    "Pour the chicken broth over the vegetables and chicken.",
    "Bake for 35-40 minutes or until the chicken is cooked through and the internal temperature reaches 165°F (74°C).",
    "Serve hot with a side of bake.",
    "Let the dish rest for 5 minutes before slicing and serving."
